OL,3,C'Changes to governance' following
OL,4,CTeesworks report
OL,6,FThe Tees Valley Mayor says that "a
OL,7,Fnumber of changes to governance" have
OL,8,Fbeen made at a major regeneration
OL,9,Fproject in Redcar.
OL,11,FIt follows a review commissioned by
OL,12,Fthe government into allegations of
OL,13,Fcorruption at Teesworks. A report
OL,14,Fpublished in January found no evidence
OL,15,Fof illegality but did make a number of
OL,16,Frecommendations to strengthen
OL,17,Fgovernance and transparency.
OL,19,FIn a progress report, Tees Valley
OL,20,FMayor Ben Houchen says recommendations
OL,21,Fhave been taken "extremely seriously."
