OL,3,C'Changes to governance' following
OL,4,CTeesworks report
OL,6,F"Teesworks is set to deliver
OL,7,Ftransformational change to Teesside,
OL,8,FDarlington and Hartlepool and this
OL,9,Fwork will now allow us to progress
OL,10,Fwith its delivery ` creating well-paid
OL,11,Fhigh-skilled jobs, attracting global
OL,12,Finvestment and growing our local
OL,13,Feconomy."
OL,15,FThe changes have been agreed with the
OL,16,Ffive constituent councils of the Tees
OL,17,FValley Combined Authority and follow a
OL,18,Freview of the 28 recommendations made
OL,19,Fin the report.
