OL,3,C'Changes to governance' following
OL,4,CTeesworks report
OL,6,FIn a letter sent to Angela Rayner,
OL,7,FDeputy Prime Minister and Secretary of
OL,8,FState for Housing, Communities and
OL,9,FLocal Government, Ben Houchen said:
OL,10,F"When the Prime Minister took office,
OL,11,FI was grateful to meet with both him
OL,12,Fand yourself to discuss this
OL,13,FGovernment's plans for the country.
OL,14,FThe unwavering message was that this
OL,15,FGovernment's central mission would be
OL,16,Fto grow our economy, a goal I share
OL,17,Fand one I am committed to working
OL,18,Fbeyond party lines to achieve.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
