OL,3,C'Changes to governance' following
OL,4,CTeesworks report
OL,6,F"It is evident that Teesworks can play
OL,7,Fa significant role in this
OL,8,FGovernment's success both economically
OL,9,Fand in the sphere of Net Zero,
OL,10,Fsomething everyone in the country
OL,11,Fshould be working towards.
OL,13,F"It is my hope that this comprehensive
OL,14,Fresponse to the Tees Valley Review can
OL,15,Fprovide a strategic reset, whereby we
OL,16,Fcan realign our goals and use the
OL,17,FTeesworks site to drive growth, create
OL,18,Fjobs, and develop the technologies of
OL,19,Fthe future."
